videos.description: Donovan Mitchell knocks down the and-1 3-pointer and lets the crowd know about it.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Mitchell fired up after and-1 three) 2021/05/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mitchell fired up after and-1 three

videos.description: Mike Conley Jr. splashes the deep 3, not to be outdone by Tyus Jones who flips in the finger roll from behind the backboard.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Mike Conley, Tyus Jones exchange impressive buckets) 2021/05/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mike Conley, Tyus Jones exchange impressive buckets

videos.description: Bojan Bogdanovic makes a business decision and gets out of the way of Kyle Anderson who crams home the dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Bojan Bogdanovic wants no part of Kyle Anderson's dunk) 2021/05/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bojan Bogdanovic wants no part of Kyle Anderson's dunk

videos.description: Donovan Mitchell sheds the defender with the step-back and knocks down the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Mitchell hits sweet step-back 3

videos.description: Ja Morant attacks the defense and wiggles his way through the lane, then finds Dillon Brooks for the easy layup.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Morant puts on a dribbling clinic, then finds Brooks for the easy one) 2021/05/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Morant puts on a dribbling clinic, then finds Brooks for the easy one

videos.description: Rudy Gobert gets the pass from Mike Conley Jr. and crams home the dunk in traffic.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Gobert finishes the dunk in traffic) 2021/05/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gobert finishes the dunk in traffic

videos.description: Ja Morant shows out with a reverse alley-oop, then throws down a monster jam in the lane as Rudy Gobert gets out of the way.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Morant puts on a dunk show in the fourth) 2021/05/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Morant puts on a dunk show in the fourth

videos.description: Donovan Mitchell's layup goes around the rim and falls, he then yells towards the crowd firing them up.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Mitchell gets the crowd hyped after icing game with layup) 2021/05/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mitchell gets the crowd hyped after icing game with layup

videos.description: Donovan Mitchell's return is overshadowed by Ja Morant who goes off for 47 points, but the Jazz prevail for a 141-129 victory.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Mitchell returns, holds off Morant as Jazz even series) 2021/05/26 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Mitchell returns, holds off Morant as Jazz even series
